# Validation

- Validate all inputs from `req.params`, `req.query`, `req.body`.
- Reject early with 400 and clear messages; don’t let invalid data reach DB layer.
- Whitelist writable fields on updates (avoid mass assignment).
- Normalize types (numbers/booleans/dates) before passing to service layer.
